videos.headline: Ole Miss takes kickoff 94 yards to the house
videos.description: Jerrion Ealy fields a kick at the Ole Miss six-yard line and breaks it to the outside, returning it all the way back for a 94-yard touchdown.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Ole Miss takes kickoff 94 yards to the house) 2019/09/14

videos.headline: Rebels' Ealy finds pay dirt for 2nd TD
videos.description: After scoring on a kick return earlier in the game, Ole Miss RB Jerrion Ealy scores on the ground for a 30-yard touchdown, giving the Rebels a 20-10 lead.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Rebels' Ealy finds pay dirt for 2nd TD) 2019/09/14

videos.headline: Pellerin makes diving grab for Ole Miss TD
videos.description: Rebels QB Matt Corral throws low to Jason Pellerin who lays out and gets his hands under the ball for a 5-yard score.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Pellerin makes diving grab for Ole Miss TD) 2019/09/14

videos.headline: Ole Miss' Phillips scores TD in 3rd straight game
videos.description: Rebels RB Scottie Phillips scores from 27 yards out, becoming the first Ole Miss player with a rushing touchdown in the team's first three games since Deuce McAllister in 2000.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Ole Miss' Phillips scores TD in 3rd straight game) 2019/09/14
